Usage: createPtnCut [-help] <cutBox> [-ptn <string>]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<cutBox>               # Specifies the lower left x ,lower left y, upper right
                       # x and upper right y coordinates of the cut area
                       # (box, required)
-ptn <string>          # Specifies a partition to create a partition cut.
                       # (string, optional)